Package: ggdesign
Type: Package
Title: Implements A Geom to Illustrate Experimental Design Structures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Charlotte", "Jones-Todd", ,
            "c.jonestodd@auckland.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1201-2781")))
Author: Charlotte M. Jones-Todd [aut, cre]
Maintainer: The package maintainer <c.jonestodd@auckland.ac.nz>
Description: The package creates a new `Geom`, `geom_design`, which can be used
    alongside `ggplot2` to depict experimental designs.
    Note that all the usual `ggplot2` machinery can be used.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1),
    ggplot2
Imports:
    grid,
    hexbin
